   
   Need to download the terraform package from the below link for Ubuntu/amazon/CentOs/RHEL
        
    $ wget https://releases.hashicorp.com/terraform/1.2.5/terraform_1.2.5_linux_amd64.zip 

   To unzip the downloaded file 

     $ unzip terraform_1.2.5_linux_amd64.zip

   Move the binary file to environment path,

     $ mv terraform /usr/local/bin 

   can check the version by 
    
      $ terraform â€“version 
